formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	It is the responsibility of management to prepare the financial statement of firm. The firm has prepared financial statement by following the mercantile method of accounting. The promoter has passed all necessary entries in accounts and reported all bank accounts in the financial statements and based on the unaudited accounts produced before us for given this certificate and relied on same for reporting to RERA Authority while certifying Form 3.
2.	The compilation & certification of figures in the said RERA Form - 3 along-with applicable annexure are based & relied on  
Latest Architects & Engineers certificates regarding estimated construction cost, Nos. of Garage/covered/Open parking as per RERA, Calculation of carpet area of each & every unit of the said project as per RERA & Percentage of completion of on-site works, 
-	Duly signed plan passed, 
-	Previous years Audited financials, 
-	Duly certified provisional financials up to (31/05/2022), 
-	Duly certified secured and unsecured loans, estimated project cost & receivables from the allottee by the management of entity and; 
-	such other information & explanations provided by the entity & proprietor/partner/director of the Entity, 
which, to the best of our knowledge and belief were necessary for the purpose of issuing this certificate.
3	We clarify that physical copy of Form No.3 & 3A contains certain explanatory and other notes to the various clauses which do not find place in the electronic Form No. 3 & 3A. In view of this, the electronic Form No.3 & 3A should be read together with all the notes appearing in the physical Form No.3 & 3A and in case of any conflict, the information and details provided in physical copy shall prevail.
4	Management of the entity has provided Customer ID, details of PAN / Aadhar Card, and Mobile Numbers of the allottees, Date of Registered Agreement for sale and Encumbrance Status and we have relied on the same while giving this certificate.
5	The promoter has directly registered Sale deed instead of agreement for sale registration hence in those cases, we have mentioned the Date of registration of Sale deed in that column. No registered agreement for sale is produced herewith by the promoter of the project.
6	The amount received from the customer / allotees are not deposited in the RERA Bank Account by the promoter which is violation of Provision of GUJARAT RERA Act, 2016 so please follow the same and deposit the said amount in RERA Bank Account.
7	The promoter has made default and not paid installment of Secured loan taken from DHFL Since Dec - 2019.
8	62 units sold by the promoter before taking loan from the DHFL hence not mortgaged to DHFL and hence in encumbrance status we have mentioned non-Encumbrance status in that units.
9	No NOC is produced while giving this certificate hence we have shown Encumbrance  Created in all the units of the project because no data available with us. 
9	As per demand and requirement of the customers, in many cases, the promoter has sold plot of land only to the customer and registered sale deed of plot of land hence we have given the said amount while giving this certificate.
